### Phase 2 — Core Auth Library Upgrades

Summary: Harden all auth library modules. Add missing modules (CSRF, fingerprint).

---

#### [MODIFY] [passwords.ts](file:///c:/Users/DELL-IN/Desktop/Projects/Ethnography-research-project/server/src/lib/auth/passwords.ts)
- Set explicit argon2id params: `memoryCost: 65536`, `timeCost: 3`, `parallelism: 4`
- Add `checkPasswordStrength()` using zxcvbn (already installed)
- Add `checkBreachedPassword()` via HaveIBeenPwned k-anonymity API
- Add minimum password rules validation (12 chars, upper, lower, digit, special)

#### [MODIFY] [tokens.ts](file:///c:/Users/DELL-IN/Desktop/Projects/Ethnography-research-project/server/src/lib/auth/tokens.ts)
