- Score thresholds: ≥0.6 require MFA, ≥0.8 block + alert

#### [MODIFY] [audit.ts](file:///c:/Users/DELL-IN/Desktop/Projects/Ethnography-research-project/server/src/lib/auth/audit.ts)
